save_dir <- file.path(dir_output, "by_pj10", "scatter_plot")
if(!dir.exists(save_dir)) dir.create(save_dir, recursive = TRUE)
ggplot(res_aval, aes(x = pj10, y = nsce, color = Model, group=Model)) +
  geom_point() +
  scale_shape_manual(values = c(17))+
  scale_color_manual(values = c("red", "blue")) + 
  coord_cartesian(ylim=c(-0.5, 1))+facet_wrap(~period) +
  labs(title = "Downstream Gauges Calibration sorted by pj 10 ") +
  xlab("pj 10 (mm)")

ggplot(data = res_aval, aes(x=class_pj10,  y= nsce, fill=Model))+ 
  geom_boxplot(show.legend=TRUE) +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(size = 10, face = "bold", hjust = 0.5), 
        legend.position="bottom",
        axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1))  + 
  coord_cartesian(ylim=c(-0.5, 1))  +
  # stat_summary(fun.data = give.n, geom = "text", fun.y = median, size = 2.7,
  #              fontface = "bold", position = position_dodge(width = 0.75))+
  ylab("Nash")+ xlab("Classes of pj10 (mm)") +
  labs(title = "Downstream Gauges - Calibration sorted by class of pj10 ") + facet_wrap(~period)

ggplot(data = res_amont, aes(x=class_pj10,  y= nsce, fill=Model))+
